\pard\sb100\sa100\qc\'b7 \'b7 \'b7 \'b7 \'b7 \par
\pard\sb100\sa100\line\line The man who came to the door was short, with red hair and red-rimmed eyes. His right hand was thrust into his coat pocket. He seemed very calm. \par
"Are you Elwood Caswell?" Rath asked. "The Elwood Caswell who bought a Regenerator early this afternoon at the Home Therapy Appliances Store?" \par
