Inside Caswell's small living room, they saw the Regenerator, glistening black and chrome, standing near the couch. It was unplugged. \par
"Have you used it?" Rath asked anxiously. \par
"Yes." \par
Follansby stepped forward. "Mr. Caswell, I don't know how to explain this, but we made a terrible mistake. The Regenerator you took was a Martian model\emdash for giving therapy to Martians." \par
